name: Alpha Synbo Meme
description: Alpha Synbo Meme (ASM) is the priori token of the Synbo Protocol, providing long-term support for the Alpha version on the BSC chain. It also serves as a key credential and weight for OG users to receive main token airdrops. Synbo is the world's first decentralized Token Issuance fund protocol based on liquidity and position proof, dedicated to becoming the most efficient, transparent, and outstanding digital asset issuance fund in the web3 space.
